<plot>In this short film adaptation of the novel of the same name by Michael L. Weinstein and Davin Seay, the experiences of both Michael and his son at the U.S. Air Force Academy are chronicled. The elder Weinstein experienced violence firsthand due to his Jewish heritage and religion, and his son experienced rampant proselytization and discrimination due to that same heritage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?658948</url></doc>
